14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 49 O.S. 2021, Section 1, is
16 amended to read as follows:
17 Section 1. A. The Secretary of State shall appoint and
18 commission in this state notaries public, who shall hold their
19 office for four (4) years.
20 B. An applicant for a new notary commission shall be eighteen
21 (18) years of age or older, a citizen of the United States, and
22 employed within this state or a legal resident of this state, and
23 shall have passed the examination required in Section 2 of this act.
24
